            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and shred apart using two forks – this is your <strong>pulled chicken</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken </strong>back to the pan and give everything a good mix up so the chicken is evenly coated in the curry sauce – this is your <strong>curried chicken enchilada filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
