    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>curried chicken enchilada filling</strong> (reserving some of the curry sauce for later) between your <strong>tortillas</strong></p><p>Roll up the <strong>tortillas</strong> tightly – these are your <strong>enchiladas</strong></p><p>Place the <strong>enchiladas</strong> in an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, with the seam side down</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
