    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spoon over the <strong>remaining curry sauce</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and <strong>nigella seeds</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-18 min or until bubbling and golden around the edges – these are your<strong> free range curried chicken</strong> <strong>enchiladas</strong></p><p>Once cooked, top with<strong> sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p>",
