    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>tamarind paste</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> in a large bowl along with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>sweet tamarind dressing</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>to the bowl with the<strong> sweet tamarind dressing </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>tamarind salad</strong></p>",
